description: Canacol Energy Ltd., an oil and gas company, engages in the exploration, development, and production of natural gas in Colombia. As of December 31, 2021, it had a total proved developed producing reserves of 236 billion cubic feet (Bcf) conventional natural gas; a total proved plus probable reserves of 607 Bcf conventional natural gas; and a total proved reserves of 368 Bcf conventional natural gas. The company was incorporated in 1970 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
ceo: Dr. Charle A. Gamba B.Sc., MSc., Ph.D.
